name: 👨‍🚀 To Escape This world... Great Artists Steal
description:
"👨‍🚀 To Escape This world... Great Artists Steal" - By Bryant W

Only one way to get on top and that is to break all the rules and never look back.

This artwork was created using old designs created back in the early 1930's collage together and remixed with patterns and other effects in photoshop.

Enjoy the future!
